  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">St. Theresa&#x2019;s Mission Hospital COVID19 Response project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">There is a threat of increased positive cases of COVID19 in Mpongwe and Masaiti districts and based on this St. Theresa Mission Hospital working to contain the spread of the virus by early detection, isolation and supportive care and treatment of COVID19 cases. This project therefore seeks to support St. Theresa Mission Hospital on the following measures that will enable the hospital support vulnerable patients during this period.
- Expansion of the provisional isolation facility (ward)
- Procurement of medical equipment
- Procurement of personal protective equipment (PPE)
- Drilling of a borehole for the improved provision of water</narrative>
  </description>
